# Artisan Marketplace

## Project Description
This project aims to develop an e-commerce platform that serves as a marketplace for artisans to showcase and sell their handcrafted goods. The platform will offer features such as product listings, user profiles, and secure payment processing.

## Target Audience
This platform is intended for artisans looking to sell their handcrafted goods, as well as consumers interested in purchasing unique, handmade items.

## User Stories
- As a user, I want to be able to browse through different categories of artisanal products.
- As a user, I want to create a profile where I can manage my listings and track my sales.
- As a user, I want to search for specific products and view detailed information about them.
- As a user, I want to be able to securely purchase items using various payment methods.
- As a user, I want to receive notifications about order status updates and promotions.

